\c 114
\s Simba raJehovha parwendo rwavaIsiraeri
\p
\v 1 Pakubuda kwaIsiraeri Imba yaJakobho ichibuda
\s pakati pavanhu vakanga
\s vanorumwe rurimi;
\p
\v 2 Judha akaitwa imba yake tsvene, Nalsiraeri ushe hwake.
\p
\v 3 Gungwa rakazviona, rikatiza; Jorodhani rwakadzokera shure.
\p
\v 4 Makomo akapembera
\s samakondobwe,
\s Nezvikomo samakwayana.
\p
\v 5 Unonzweiko iwe gungwa, zvaunotiza iwe?
\s Newe Jorodhani, zvaunodzokera shure?
\p
\v 6 Nemi makomo, zvamunopembera samakondobwe;
\s Nemi zvikomo, samakwayana?
\p
\v 7 Bvunda iwe pasi, pamberi paShe, Pamberi paMwari waJakobho;
\p
\v 8 Iye akashandura dombo, rikava
\s dziva remvura,
